flowchart LR
  Sim[CombatSimulation\n确定性玩法系统] -->|EffectEvent| Queue[EffectEventQueue]
  Queue --> Registry[VfxRegistry\nJSON 效果配置]
  Registry --> Guard[ReadabilityGuard\n保护判定点/敌弹]
  Guard --> Pool[ParticlePool\n粒子对象池]
  Guard --> Shake[ScreenShakeManager\nrender-only]
  Guard --> Audio[ProceduralAudioBus\nWebAudio]
  Pool --> Renderer[CanvasRenderer\nRenderLayerStack]
  Shake --> Renderer
  Audio --> Output[Speakers]
  Renderer --> Screen[屏幕]

  Sim -.不会直接创建粒子/播放音效.-> Registry
